OL,3,CWorkers at Tetley Tea factory walk out
OL,4,Cover pay
OL,6,FPaul Clark, GMB organiser, said "This
OL,7,Floyal, predominantly female workforce
OL,8,Fhas endured year after year of real
OL,9,Fterms pay cuts.
OL,11,F"Now they have had enough."
OL,13,FThe strike, which also took place on
OL,14,FFriday, is the first of its kind to
OL,15,Fhit Tetley Tea at the site.
OL,17,FTata Consumer Products said: "We are
OL,18,Fdisappointed with the decision to
OL,19,Fstrike particularly when we have two
OL,20,Foffers on the table.
